    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a P2P IPTV Usage for Resource Location And Discovery (RELOAD). The IPTV Usage provides the functionality of IPTV servers in a fully-distributed system using P2PSIP RELOAD. The IPTV Usage provides the metadata storage, channel peer list storage, and channel peer group storage using the P2PSIP overlay. This documents defines three kinds about these usages.</t>
